Package it.uniroma2.sel.simlab.jeqn.serviceCenters

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InfiniteServer
    Implements the simulation logic of a EQN Infinite Server
    NonPreemptiveServiceCenter
    Implements an EQN Service Center that operates with a Non-Preemptive policy, i.e. the processing of a user is not interrupted by incoming user with higher priorities
    PreEmptiveServiceCenter
    Implements an EQN Service Center that allows to interrupt the processing of a user as an higher priority user incomes.
    ServiceCenter
    Defines the common interface, method, and the general behavior of Service Centers.
    Sink
    Defines the EQN Sink entity.
